<span id="freeTextContainer11120648333029341924">A lovely book that has stood the test of time.<br/><br/>2020: Read this aloud to the kids as it&apos;s on the Battle of the Books list this year for my daughter. I had forgotten how much is covered in such a slim book, yet how fast it goes. Also the casual cruelty of both Jess&apos;s family and bullies at school, not to mention how Leslie and Jess retaliate. Interesting. </span>
