<div id="review_1550939036" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1550939036" />
    <a title="Jananie (thisstoryaintover)" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/11588992-jananie-thisstoryaintover"><img alt="Jananie (thisstoryaintover)" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1527221743p2/11588992.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1550939036?book_show_action=true">Feb 16, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jananie (thisstoryaintover)" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jananie (thisstoryaintover)" href="/user/show/11588992-jananie-thisstoryaintover">Jananie (thisstoryaintover)</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback " href="/book/show/35097580-bridge-to-terabithia">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/11588992-jananie-thisstoryaintover?shelf=books-i-own">books-i-own</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1550939036" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9603451546790902573">I remember watching the movie for this book when I was a kid and finding it the most wondrous thing. This story has influenced my life far more than I can express. Reading the book brought all those memories and dreams back, right when I needed them most. I recommend this book to anyone who has ever been a kid before, and dreamed, and wished, and had friends, and lost them, and desired beyond belief to have them back. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


